<A>__{wilson steps out into the late sunlight and the heat of the day. a slow motion moment while he gets acclimatized. he wouldn't have ever felt quite this kind of heat before. after such a rigorously air conditioned interior. or seen cops wearing guns on their belts. or black cops, for that matter, with guns on their belts. or seen people as fat as americans on their home turf. things someone from england notices immediately, whether consciously at first or not.}
